snippet.title: A Defense Lawyer Discusses the Marilyn Manson Case & Recent Police “Raid” & Search Warrant
snippet.description:
Marilyn Manson / Legal Analysis /Raid / Search Warrant / Allegations / Evan Rachel Wood / Esme Bianco / Innocent / 

I spoke with criminal defense attorney Andrea Burkhart for her legal analysis on the Marilyn Manson situation and the recent LAPD / LASD search of one of his properties. 

For more on the Marilyn Manson allegations and my analysis, see this playlist: https://m.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLy922tRlXtvgvbmqaIPRx_nVJuK5qs4qK
